rows.label: qst201408_msg0001
rows.name: You there, be quiet!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0002
rows.name:
Even if you are lovely girls,
we cannot overlook you disturbing
our sleep at this hour!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0003
rows.name:
Staying up late is bad for your skin!
For our sake, please go to bed!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0004
rows.name: Rinne!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0005
rows.name:
Hikari and I are having a Girl
Power competition right now!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0006
rows.name:
You are not listening to us
at all... But a Girl Power
competition sounds amusing.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0007
rows.name:
We want you to judge which of us,
me or Zakuro, has more Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0008
rows.name:
We see... Very well. We
shall be the judge!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0023
rows.name:
Then, shall we talk
about crushes again?

rows.label: qst201408_msg0024
rows.name: You really like that topic...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0009
rows.name: Rinne, what's your ideal type of man?

rows.label: qst201408_msg0010
rows.name:
Good question. Rinne is always
about girls, so I'm curious
what she thinks about men.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0011
rows.name:
What we seek in a man is,
first and foremost, money!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0012
rows.name: M-Money...?

rows.label: qst201408_msg0013
rows.name:
A man is only a man if he has the
means to provide for a woman!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0014
rows.name: However, means alone are not enough.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0015
rows.name:
If he cannot escort us with style
and observe proper manners, he
is not worthy of our company.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0016
rows.name:
For example, the ability to make delicious tea
is essential. We also want the bath scrubbed
spotless, and a villa near a beautiful lake.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0017
rows.name: Well, this is quite...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0018
rows.name:
The bar is set so high, I
can't quite keep up...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0019
rows.name:
We have mastered the art of
being a lady, so the man by
our side must be top-class...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0020
rows.name:
It's kind of hard to get a
conversation going here...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0021
rows.name: We picked the wrong person...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0022
rows.name:
Let's hope for someone
else next time...
